&lt;DIV&gt;I was pulling in the LDoN the other day on Level 70 Normals using the 65 spells for their proximity supression and found that I had tonnes of resists using it. After the upteenth resist and a couple of agro from resists at Cha &amp;gt; 300 I changed to Placate. Ever since I NEVER got a resist. Not one. No resist means no check on your charisma.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;From that experience Placate is a great tool for those mobs that are magic resistant. Despite the spells (0) modifier my experiences on resist rates were startling.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
